'''Club Deportivo Valle del Chota''' is an [[Ecuador]]ian professional [[association football|football]] club based in [[Ibarra, Ecuador|Ibarra]]. It is the current winner of the [[Ecuadorian Segunda Categoría|Segunda Categoría]], for which it has gained promotion to the second-level [[Ecuadorian Serie B|Serie B]] for the 2011 season.

