===Countries===
* Only on three occasions has the final of the tournament involved two teams from the same country: ** 1971 Yugoslavia: [[VK Partizan|Partizan]] vs [[HAVK Mladost]] ''4''–''4'' ** 1993 Croatia: [[VK Jadran Split|Jadran Split]] vs [[HAVK Mladost]] 13–12 (7–8, 6–4) ** 1998 Italy: [[CN Posillipo|Posillipo]] vs [[ASP Waterpolis Pescara|Pescara]] 8–6 * The country providing the highest number of wins is ''Yugoslavia'' with 13 victories, shared by two teams, [[VK Partizan|Partizan]] (6), [[HAVK Mladost]] (6) and [[VK Jug Dubrovnik|Jug Dubrovnik]] (1)
