{{Unsourced|date=May 2013}}
'''Gbikinti FC''' is a [[Togo]]lese [[football (soccer)|football]] club, based in Bassar. They play in the top division in Togolese football. Stade de Bassar, which has capacity for 1,000 people, is the venue of Gbikinti.

