'''Geofredo de Sousa Cheung''', also known in Chinese as '''Chit Un Cheung''' (born 18 May 1979) is a [[Macau|Macanese]] [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Midfielder (football)|midfielder]] for [[C.D. Monte Carlo]] in the [[Campeonato da 1ª Divisão do Futebol]].<ref>{{NFT player|pid=3981}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.footballdatabase.eu/football.joueurs.chit-un.cheung.67394.en.html |title=Football : Chit Un Cheung |publisher=Footballdatabase.eu |date=1979-05-18 |accessdate=2013-12-11}}</ref>
