{{Infobox football biography | name= Samir Bertin d'Avesnes | fullname = | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1986|4|15}} | birth_place = [[Moroni, Comoros|Moroni]], [[Comoros]] | height = {{convert|1.78|m|ftin|0|abbr=on}} | currentclub = [[FC Aregno-Calvi]] | clubnumber = 18 | position = [[Forward (association football)|Striker]] | youthyears1= 1999–2002 | youthclubs1= US Endoume Marseille | years1 = 2002–2006 | years2 = 2002–2008 | years3 = 2008–2009 | years4 = 2009–2011 | years5 = 2011– | clubs1 = SC Bastia B | clubs2 = [[SC Bastia]] | clubs3 = [[Croix de Savoie Gaillard]] | clubs4 = [[AS Beauvais Oise]] | clubs5 = [[FC Aregno-Calvi]] | caps1 = 62 | goals1 = 19 | caps2 = 25 | goals2 = 1 | caps3 = 24 | goals3 = 1 | caps4 = 55 | goals4 = 4 | caps5 = 18 | goals5 = 0 | nationalyears1 = 2002–2004 | nationalteam1 = [[France national under-17 football team|France U-17]] | nationalcaps1 = 10 | nationalgoals1 = 6 | nationalyears2 = 2004 | nationalteam2 = [[France national under-18 football team|France U-18]] | nationalcaps2 = 20 | nationalgoals2 = 6 | nationalyears3 = 2011 | nationalteam3 = [[Comoros national football team|Comoros]] | nationalcaps3 = 1 | nationalgoals3 = 0<ref>{{NFT player|id=45546|accessdate= }}</ref> | pcupdate = | ntupdate = }}
'''Samir Bertin d'Avesnes''' (born April 15, 1986 in [[Moroni, Comoros|Moroni]]) is a [[Comoros|Comorian]] footballer, who plays for [[FC Aregno-Calvi]].<ref>[http://www.corsefootball.fr/clubs-dh-cfa-cfa-2/calvi/2011-2012/ 2011/2012 – corse football!]</ref><ref>{{Soccerway|s-bertin-davesnes/71256|accessdate=9 January 2015}}</ref>
== Club career == He played for French Ligue 2 club [[SC Bastia]] from 2002 to 2008. However, in August 2008, he resiliated his contract with SC Bastia and signed to [[Croix-de-Savoie]]. After one year with Savoie, signed in summer 2009 for [[AS Beauvais Oise]].<ref>[https://www.lequipe.fr/Football/FootballFicheJoueur18968.html Player profile – L'Equipe.fr] </ref>
== International career == Bertin d'Avesnes has played for the U-18 [[France national football team]]. The [[Striker (football)|striker]] earned one nationalcap for the Comoros senior national football team.<ref>{{FIFA player|351012}}</ref>
